      "title": "Memory saturation \u2014 swap in use (S)",
      "description": "SwapTotal - SwapFree per node. PSI is unavailable (node_pressure_* does not exist), so bytes of swap in use is shown as the memory-pressure proxy; any non-zero value means the node has spilled to swap.",
